.DT
is_allowed_to_sell
Disk World creator help
is_allowed_to_sell

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
is_allowed_to_sell -  This method checks to see if this item is allowed to be sold in this shop.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int is_allowed_to_sell(object * obs,
string name,
string * sellable_names)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^obs%^RESET%^ - the objects to check
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the name of the person doing the selling
%^BOLD%^sellable_names%^RESET%^ - the names of the items to sell

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/inherit/craft_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method checks to see if this item is allowed to be sold in this shop.
It assumes it is called from a add_command() method and sets up fail
messages accordingly.
.EP

